  "response": "After the debate aired, you could typically watch it on several platforms:\n\n1. **Fox News Website**: They often provide full debates or highlights for streaming on their official site.\n2. **YouTube**: Fox News may upload the debate in segments or as a full video on their official YouTube channel.\n3. **Streaming Services**: Depending on your subscription, platforms like Hulu or Fox Nation might have the debate available.\n4. **Social Media**: Check Fox News' Facebook or Twitter accounts, as they may share clips or highlights.\n\nFor the specific debate, you could try searching these platforms to see if it\u2019s still available for viewing.",
